Coming Out - Program 1: Out of Innocence (with Wayne Blakely) - This is program 1 of a 13-part series produced by White Horse Media entitled, "Coming Out: Former Gays Testify of God’s Saving Love." Program 1 contains the thrilling testimony of Wayne Blakely, who was interviewed by Steve Wohlberg. Order the "Coming Out" series today!

The entire 13-part "Coming Out" series is available on DVD here: http://whitehorsemedia.com/store/40-homosexuality/112-coming-out-former-gays-testify-of-gods-saving-love.html. Order online or call 208-448-4446.
